WEBVTT

00:01.402 --> 00:03.737
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da,
ba-da-ba-da-ba ♪

00:03.771 --> 00:05.239
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da
Let's go!

00:05.273 --> 00:06.907
♪ We'll be there

00:06.940 --> 00:09.577
♪ A wink and a smile
and a great old time ♪

00:09.610 --> 00:11.812
♪ Yeah, we'll be there

00:11.845 --> 00:13.914
♪ Wherever we are,
there's some fun to be found ♪

00:13.947 --> 00:16.217
♪ We'll be there
when you turn that corner ♪

00:16.250 --> 00:17.551
♪ We'll jump out the bush

00:17.585 --> 00:19.253
♪ With a big bear hug
and a smile ♪

00:19.287 --> 00:20.721
♪ We'll be there

00:27.295 --> 00:30.431
[ Thunder claps, wolf howling ]

00:34.102 --> 00:35.769
[ Hooting ]

00:37.271 --> 00:38.772
Boo!
[ Laughs ]

00:38.806 --> 00:40.108
Happy Halloween!

00:40.141 --> 00:41.609
Did I scare you?

00:41.642 --> 00:43.211
Ah, of course I did.

00:43.244 --> 00:46.780
But if that didn't do the trick,
maybe ol' Charlie could treat

00:46.814 --> 00:49.283
you with some scary stories.
[ Laughs ]

00:49.317 --> 00:50.951
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa,
hold on a minute.

00:50.984 --> 00:53.621
I promise, these stories
ain't for babies.

00:53.654 --> 00:54.955
Now, come on.

00:54.988 --> 00:57.358
The first story started
on a night just like this,

00:57.391 --> 01:01.295
when three bear brothers
got a special delivery.

01:02.496 --> 01:03.864
Grizzly:
Ah! Adorable!

01:03.897 --> 01:05.065
Panda:
Oh, so cute!

01:05.099 --> 01:06.267
Where'd you
get these, Pan?

01:06.300 --> 01:07.735
Oh, I found them
online.

01:07.768 --> 01:10.404
Ah! They look just like little
us-es! [ Giggles ]

01:10.438 --> 01:11.872
Huh? What's the little heart
for?

01:11.905 --> 01:14.808
It's says, "Put your essence
into the heart locket

01:14.842 --> 01:19.813
and your oso adorable
will become beary special."

01:19.847 --> 01:21.915
E-Essence?
Like our blood?

01:21.949 --> 01:23.217
Eh, maybe just hair
will work.

01:23.251 --> 01:25.153
Oh, yeah.
So, we take a hair...

01:25.186 --> 01:26.320
[ Doing! ]
Ow!

01:26.354 --> 01:28.489
Place it
in the heart locket...

01:28.522 --> 01:30.158
Ice Bear: Put locket
of love inside.

01:30.191 --> 01:31.325
With care.

01:31.359 --> 01:33.161
Oh, I'm so
plush and cute!

01:33.194 --> 01:35.263
I love you,
little Panda.

01:35.296 --> 01:36.830
Little Panda:
I love you, too!

01:36.864 --> 01:39.933
Whoa! The website didn't say
anything about them talking.

01:39.967 --> 01:42.836
Little Grizzly: I love to
make friends and eat snacks.

01:42.870 --> 01:46.807
Ha, ha, yeah, that's pretty
accurate to my essence, I guess.

01:46.840 --> 01:48.176
Little Ice Bear:
Ice Bear loves hugs.

01:48.209 --> 01:49.810
Hug me.

01:49.843 --> 01:52.346
Ice Bear would not say that.
This is not Ice Bear's essence.

01:52.380 --> 01:54.982
Little Grizzly:
I looove picking my nose.

01:55.015 --> 01:56.684
Little Panda:
I like dressing up as a cat,

01:56.717 --> 01:59.019
[whispering]
when no one is looking.

01:59.052 --> 02:00.988
Well, these are obviously
defective.

02:01.021 --> 02:02.523
Oh, yeah, no,
totally defective.

02:02.556 --> 02:04.958
Well, I guess we'll just send
them back in the morning.

02:04.992 --> 02:06.160
How 'bout some grub?

02:06.194 --> 02:07.361
Ice Bear will
make casserole.

02:07.395 --> 02:08.829
Oh, sweet.
I'm down for that.

02:08.862 --> 02:11.299
Oh, hey, guys -- this time,
can we make it vegetarian?

02:11.332 --> 02:13.634
I hate picking out
all the chicken and...

02:13.667 --> 02:16.337
[ Sizzling ]

02:16.370 --> 02:17.838
Ooh, boy --
smells so good!

02:17.871 --> 02:19.039
Thanks, brother.

02:19.072 --> 02:21.209
Mmm. Huh, thought
I grabbed silverware.

02:21.242 --> 02:22.876
Uh, could you grab me
a fork, please?

02:22.910 --> 02:24.044
Ice Bear
got you covered.

02:24.077 --> 02:25.279
Huh?

02:25.313 --> 02:26.814
[ Indistinct whispering ]

02:26.847 --> 02:28.182
Lil Panda?

02:28.216 --> 02:30.218
That's weird.
How'd you get out of the...

02:30.251 --> 02:32.019
[ Gasps ] They're gone!
What the heck?

02:32.052 --> 02:34.388
Where did the dolls go?
This doesn't make any sense.

02:34.422 --> 02:36.290
What's going on?
The other dolls are missing

02:36.324 --> 02:37.725
What?
We just put them away.

02:37.758 --> 02:40.060
Maybe they're under the table
or something.

02:40.093 --> 02:42.230
Hmm. You find anything?
Nothing.

02:42.263 --> 02:43.531
Ice Bear found
lost controller.

02:43.564 --> 02:45.299
Ooh, been looking for that.

02:45.333 --> 02:46.700
[ Whispering ]

02:46.734 --> 02:49.803
Uh, wasn't Lil Panda just
sitting on this table?

02:49.837 --> 02:51.171
Yes, yes, he was.

02:51.205 --> 02:52.573
Ice Bear leaving.

02:52.606 --> 02:54.475
Yep, I'm with him. I'm
gonna give Tabes a call.

02:54.508 --> 02:55.909
She's good with this
kind of creepy stuff.

02:55.943 --> 02:57.144
[ Phone ringing ]

02:57.177 --> 02:58.679
[ Screams ]
[ Gasps ]

02:58.712 --> 03:01.081
Tabes: Speak.
This is Ranger Tabes.

03:01.114 --> 03:02.750
Oh. [ Laughs ]
Never mind, Tabes.

03:02.783 --> 03:04.252
Talk to you later.
[ Phone beeps ]

03:04.285 --> 03:05.486
I didn't know
they could do that.

03:05.519 --> 03:08.756
It's kind of cute,
but also creepy.

03:08.789 --> 03:10.591
Little Ice Bear: It's time for dinner.
Let's eat.

03:10.624 --> 03:12.360
Little Panda:
Spoonful of sugar?

03:12.393 --> 03:13.661
Little Grizzly:
Let's spread some cheer.

03:13.694 --> 03:15.396
[ Screams ]
Not cute! Not cute!

03:15.429 --> 03:17.231
All: It's time for dinner!

03:17.265 --> 03:18.599
Let's eat.

03:18.632 --> 03:19.933
[ Screams ]

03:21.134 --> 03:23.904
[ Screaming ]

03:23.937 --> 03:25.606
[ Panting ]

03:25.639 --> 03:27.641
Little Grizzly: 'Sup, bro? Ahh!

03:30.478 --> 03:32.112
Little Ice Bear:
Ice Bear forgot his fork.

03:32.145 --> 03:33.747
Ice Bear hungry.

03:40.053 --> 03:41.589
[ Panting ]

03:47.895 --> 03:50.130
Where are you?

03:50.163 --> 03:51.399
Ahh!

03:51.432 --> 03:52.800
Little Panda:
I found you!

03:52.833 --> 03:54.468
Miki-chan, no!

03:56.837 --> 04:00.240
[ Laughs ]
I love playing hide and seek!

04:01.975 --> 04:03.777
[ Grinding ]

04:03.811 --> 04:05.813
Little Ice Bear: Ice Bear thinks
we got off on wrong...foot!

04:05.846 --> 04:08.282
Ice Bear wants to
break the...ice!

04:14.488 --> 04:16.223
[ Winding down ]
Let's get cook...

04:16.256 --> 04:18.058
Whoa.
[ Panda screams ]

04:18.091 --> 04:19.493
Stay away, stay back!

04:19.527 --> 04:23.397
Little Panda: Ready or not,
here I come!

04:23.431 --> 04:25.599
Ahh!
Oh, you saved me.

04:25.633 --> 04:27.401
Is it dead?

04:27.435 --> 04:29.102
That's cheating.
You're no fun.

04:29.136 --> 04:30.304
Not dead.
Not dead.

04:30.338 --> 04:31.772
Aah!
Hold on!

04:31.805 --> 04:34.074
There's got to be an off switch
or something.

04:34.107 --> 04:35.309
Heart is off switch.

04:35.343 --> 04:37.745
Ahh!
What the -- ow!

04:37.778 --> 04:39.012
Hyah!

04:39.046 --> 04:41.114
Oh! The heart!

04:41.148 --> 04:42.316
Ha, ha!

04:42.350 --> 04:43.517
Hug me, hug me!

04:43.551 --> 04:45.486
[ Winding down ]
Hug me...

04:47.120 --> 04:48.288
I think that did it.

04:48.322 --> 04:49.757
Aah!

04:49.790 --> 04:51.525
Ice Bear
not taking chances.

04:51.559 --> 04:52.960
Grizzly:
Help, help!

04:52.993 --> 04:54.161
Grizz!

04:54.194 --> 04:56.263
Ah! Guys, he's me,
but stronger!

04:56.296 --> 04:58.532
Get off of him!
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow.

04:58.566 --> 04:59.600
Ha!

04:59.633 --> 05:01.869
Gah! I thought we were bros,
lil bro.

05:01.902 --> 05:03.036
I mean, I loved you!

05:03.070 --> 05:04.438
Little Grizzly:
I do love you, bro.

05:04.472 --> 05:05.973
[ Menacingly ] To pieces.

05:06.006 --> 05:07.541
[ Growls ] Ah!

05:07.575 --> 05:09.009
I know karate, bro.

05:09.042 --> 05:10.344
I'll kick your face off.

05:10.378 --> 05:11.545
We can't hold him long!

05:11.579 --> 05:13.714
Play time is over!

05:13.747 --> 05:16.049
Wait, no --
my essence!

05:16.083 --> 05:17.785
Time to return
the favor.

05:17.818 --> 05:19.587
[ Shatters ]

05:27.761 --> 05:28.996
Oh, man.

05:29.029 --> 05:30.398
I'm never buying anything
off that website again.

05:30.431 --> 05:31.799
Oh, yeah, brother.

05:31.832 --> 05:32.833
[ Knocking ]

05:32.866 --> 05:35.235
Hey, fellas.
I got your phone call.

05:35.268 --> 05:36.870
Oh. [ Laughs ]
It's you, Tabes.

05:36.904 --> 05:39.306
[ Laughs nervously ] Yeah,
we had a little thing earlier,

05:39.339 --> 05:40.741
but, uh,
everything's fine now.

05:40.774 --> 05:42.543
Well, I heard you
talking about dolls,

05:42.576 --> 05:45.045
and I wanted to show you
Little Tabes!

05:45.078 --> 05:46.480
Little Tabes:
Let's serve some...

05:46.514 --> 05:48.081
[ Menacingly ]
...justice.

05:48.115 --> 05:50.017
[ Screaming ]

05:50.050 --> 05:52.486
[ Laughs ] Pretty scary stuff,
right?

05:52.520 --> 05:54.187
[ Laughs ]
Well, that ain't nothing

05:54.221 --> 05:55.489
compared to the next story.

05:55.523 --> 05:57.591
This one's about
a real strange creature --

05:57.625 --> 06:01.094
a 10-year-old girl
who goes to college.

06:01.128 --> 06:02.963
Ooooooooh!
[ Wolf howling ]

06:04.632 --> 06:07.100
Interestingly enough,
the common mythology is that

06:07.134 --> 06:09.603
being bitten by a lycanthrope
will turn you into one.

06:09.637 --> 06:12.172
Then how do you get released
from this curse?

06:12.205 --> 06:13.707
Anyone?

06:13.741 --> 06:15.409
Yes. In ancient times,
it was believe that werewolves

06:15.443 --> 06:17.277
are vulnerable
to silver objects.

06:17.310 --> 06:18.512
[ Coughing ]
Nerd!

06:18.546 --> 06:20.013
[ Stifled laughter ]

06:20.047 --> 06:23.617
Class! Yes, that's right.
Very nice, Chloe.

06:23.651 --> 06:25.453
Yeah, very nice,
prodigy.

06:25.486 --> 06:26.720
[ Grumbles ]

06:26.754 --> 06:28.956
I mean, we're in college,
for Pete's sake.

06:28.989 --> 06:31.725
These guys are still acting
like they're in junior high

06:31.759 --> 06:33.561
or something!
Ugh!

06:34.562 --> 06:36.263
Yeah, but you were never
in junior high.

06:36.296 --> 06:37.465
I know
what it's like!

06:37.498 --> 06:39.132
I've seen these type
of kids on TV.

06:39.166 --> 06:41.368
Now, now, they're just jealous
that you're smart.

06:41.401 --> 06:42.870
Yeah, Chloe,
just be a bigger person.

06:42.903 --> 06:44.404
And once you're a bigger person,
you can beat them up.

06:44.438 --> 06:45.606
Baaah!

06:45.639 --> 06:47.207
On that note --

06:47.240 --> 06:49.042
Can I have your ice cream
if you're not gonna finish it?

06:49.076 --> 06:50.243
Sure, go ahead.

06:50.277 --> 06:51.545
Oh, you the best,
Chloe!

06:51.579 --> 06:52.946
[ Chomp! ]
Ahh!

06:52.980 --> 06:54.147
Grizz, you bit me!

06:54.181 --> 06:55.916
Oh, shoot, I'm so sorry!
I didn't see your hand!

06:55.949 --> 06:57.317
It was hiding behind
that ice-cream scoop!

06:57.350 --> 06:58.586
No worries.
It's just a scratch.

06:58.619 --> 06:59.987
Oh, are you sure
you're okay?

07:00.020 --> 07:01.221
Yeah, don't worry.

07:01.254 --> 07:02.690
I'm gonna go
wash it off.

07:03.991 --> 07:05.158
[ Faucet squeaks ]

07:05.192 --> 07:07.327
Hmm.

07:07.360 --> 07:09.229
Huh?

07:09.262 --> 07:12.232
Ahh...what the!

07:12.265 --> 07:14.267
Ah, aah!

07:14.301 --> 07:16.003
[ Screams ]
My nose!

07:16.036 --> 07:18.839
[ Screams, grunts ]

07:18.872 --> 07:20.741
[ Screams ]

07:20.774 --> 07:23.611
Uhh...my hands! Ahh!

07:25.546 --> 07:27.781
Got to go, guys!
Bye! See ya!

07:27.815 --> 07:29.282
[ Door opens, slams ]
What's up with her?

07:29.316 --> 07:31.685
Ice Bear senses...
spookiness.

07:31.719 --> 07:33.120
-Susan?
-Here.

07:33.153 --> 07:34.321
-Daniel?
-Yep.

07:34.354 --> 07:35.523
Kyle?
-Present.

07:35.556 --> 07:37.090
-Chloe?
-[ Growls ]

07:37.124 --> 07:38.358
Hm? Chloe?

07:38.391 --> 07:39.993
[ Clears throat ]
I mean, "Present!"

07:40.027 --> 07:41.662
Whoa, what's up
with your hand?

07:41.695 --> 07:42.863
Stop it!
Ahh!

07:42.896 --> 07:44.598
Whoa!
Check out her ears!

07:44.632 --> 07:47.034
[ Gasps ]
[ Indistinct chatter ]

07:47.067 --> 07:50.437
Boy: Oh, you have no idea how
awesome you are right now, Chloe.

07:50.470 --> 07:51.639
Really?

07:51.672 --> 07:53.874
[ Indistinct chatter ]

07:53.907 --> 07:56.777
Hmm...

07:56.810 --> 07:59.212
Huh. Can't believe Chloe invited
us to get boba on a weeknight.

07:59.246 --> 08:00.848
Maybe she finished studying
early or...

08:00.881 --> 08:03.050
[ Dance music plays ]
Whoa! What's going on?

08:03.083 --> 08:06.887
Crowd: Go, Chloe! Go, Chloe!
Go, go! Go, Chloe!

08:06.920 --> 08:08.522
[ Cheering ]
[ Growls ]

08:08.556 --> 08:10.758
[ Cheering ]

08:15.696 --> 08:17.831
[ Roaring ]

08:17.865 --> 08:19.166
-Hey!
-Chloe, what happened to you?

08:19.199 --> 08:20.901
I turned into a werebear
after you bit me!

08:20.934 --> 08:23.571
Now, everybody loves me
and wants to party with me!

08:23.604 --> 08:24.872
-Whoa, really?
-Come on!

08:24.905 --> 08:26.807
Let's go have
some bear times.

08:26.840 --> 08:28.676
Ice Bear ready to have
Ice Bear times.

08:28.709 --> 08:30.510
Chloe: Hey, guys!
Meet my fam.

08:30.544 --> 08:32.345
Wassup, fellas.
This is my dad.

08:32.379 --> 08:33.881
Wait, what?
No, no, no, no.

08:33.914 --> 08:36.316
I just bit her hand
and she turned into a werebear.

08:36.349 --> 08:38.886
We're not technically related,
although I view her as family.

08:38.919 --> 08:40.320
Ice Bear not ready
to be father.

08:40.353 --> 08:42.590
I'm thirsty!
Me want boba.

08:42.623 --> 08:43.924
Chloe,
where are you going?

08:43.957 --> 08:45.926
Oh, Master Bear?
Can you bite me, too?

08:45.959 --> 08:47.695
Yeah, I want to be cool
like Chloe, too!

08:47.728 --> 08:49.897
[ Growls ]
Ahh!

08:51.965 --> 08:53.601
[ Growls ]

08:53.634 --> 08:54.835
Seriously, dude,
come on.

08:54.868 --> 08:56.236
Just bite me
right here.

08:56.269 --> 08:57.437
[ Chloe growling ]

08:57.470 --> 08:59.406
Help! Ahh!
Ow! Help me!

08:59.439 --> 09:00.741
Chloe!

09:00.774 --> 09:02.743
Aw, her feral bear instincts
are kicking in!

09:02.776 --> 09:04.444
Out of my way!
Chloe, stop!

09:04.477 --> 09:05.613
Grab her arms!

09:05.646 --> 09:07.214
Ah! Hold still, Chloe!

09:07.247 --> 09:08.415
[ Growling ]

09:08.448 --> 09:12.185
Whoa, whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa!

09:12.219 --> 09:13.987
[ Screaming ]

09:18.558 --> 09:19.727
What do we do?

09:19.760 --> 09:20.928
Call the popo
or something!

09:20.961 --> 09:22.529
Oh, yeah.
Uhh...

09:22.562 --> 09:24.264
[ Screams ]
[ Growls ]

09:24.297 --> 09:25.465
[ Screaming ]

09:25.498 --> 09:26.634
[ Roars ]

09:26.667 --> 09:28.135
Professor: Stop!

09:30.470 --> 09:35.142
What a shame. My own student,
turned into a beast.

09:35.175 --> 09:36.877
[ Growls, roars ]

09:36.910 --> 09:39.112
Ha!
Didn't I teach you, Chloe?

09:39.146 --> 09:42.482
No werewolf
can withstand silver.

09:42.515 --> 09:43.884
Ah!

09:43.917 --> 09:45.085
Chloe!

09:45.118 --> 09:46.286
Don't hurt her!

09:46.319 --> 09:48.055
-Chloe!
-Chloe, you okay?

09:48.088 --> 09:50.490
Oh, Chloe.
Please, do something!

09:50.523 --> 09:51.725
What have you done?

09:51.759 --> 09:52.926
You monster.

09:52.960 --> 09:54.127
Ice Bear
does not forgive.

09:54.161 --> 09:56.096
Do not worry, bears.
Pain is good.

09:56.129 --> 09:59.266
It means the evil inside her
is reacting to it.

09:59.299 --> 10:00.934
What does that even mean?

10:02.535 --> 10:04.237
Um, Chloe?

10:04.271 --> 10:06.106
[ Grunts, roars ]

10:06.139 --> 10:07.507
What? Impossible!

10:07.540 --> 10:09.643
What kind of wolf
bit her?

10:09.677 --> 10:11.344
-Hey.
-Wait, what?

10:11.378 --> 10:12.913
So, she's not a werewolf?

10:12.946 --> 10:15.783
Um, maybe more like a werebear,
to be exact?

10:15.816 --> 10:18.618
Ohh...well, in that case,
I can't really help.

10:18.652 --> 10:20.587
I only specialize
in werewolves.

10:20.620 --> 10:22.055
Can't help ya.

10:23.490 --> 10:25.125
Uhh...thanks?

10:25.158 --> 10:26.960
[ Growls ]

10:30.163 --> 10:32.032
Hey, look --
She's full bear now.

10:32.065 --> 10:34.868
What do we do?
She has class tomorrow.

10:37.070 --> 10:39.039
"H."

10:39.072 --> 10:40.841
Rawr?

10:40.874 --> 10:43.176
Oh, well.
Close enough, right?

10:44.211 --> 10:46.847
Charlie: Oooooooooh!

10:48.581 --> 10:51.819
Well, thanks for giving
ol' Charlie's stories a listen.

10:51.852 --> 10:53.987
So, what'd ya'll think?

10:54.021 --> 10:57.390
[ Clicks ]
[ Screaming ]

10:57.424 --> 10:58.558
Ooh! Candy!

10:58.591 --> 10:59.793
Happy Halloween!

10:59.827 --> 11:02.195
[ Munch, munch ]

11:03.931 --> 11:07.768
♪♪

11:15.175 --> 11:16.309
[ Furious typing ]

11:16.343 --> 11:18.045
-Done!
-Done!
